{"type": "article", "id": 56764, "title": "伦敦时装周上模特穿着吸乳器？可穿戴且免手动｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-09-25T22:40:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 53008, "name": "Studio davidpompa"}, {"id": 53009, "name": "LifeProof"}, {"id": 53010, "name": "Elvie"}, {"id": 53011, "name": "Anton Repponen"}, {"id": 53012, "name": "Carolina Ortega"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 136, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180925222512XTIHvD1JY9BxOR2W.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'Helvetica Neue'; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Breast Pump by Elvie </h3><p>在伦敦时装周上，时装品牌 Marta Jakubowsk 的模特 Valeria Garcia 穿上这一季最新内衣后，内搭了一个吸乳器，出自品牌 Elvie，自称是有史以来第一款可穿戴的吸乳器。</p><p>Elive 是一家伦敦的初创企业，它因为一款凯格尔球而被人们所熟知。这款由前戴森工程师设计的 Elvie 吸乳器是无线、免手动的，它是一个封闭系统，还配备可充电电池。它能容纳 140 克的乳汁，每次吸一个乳房。</p><p>值得一提的是，Elvie 的吸乳器不需要专利储奶袋，乳汁会直接进入机子，接着手机 app 就会告诉你某一边储满了奶，可以直接把每一滴乳汁泵进奶瓶。此外，它还声称是静音的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222534t0pisb7SL9vMZKfn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664552\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222536CgEMkhKz2yZtlGTc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222534zWlky57qdNDxfZAT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222534CKgvlJ6yYI3OZDf7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018092522253752xXrVZpCyhsMgi6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/09/24/elvie-wearable-breast-pump-silent-wireless-news-technology/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>SLɅM, NËXT &amp; FRĒ by LifeProof</h3><p>苹果最近发布了 iPhone 系列新品，配件品牌 LifeProof 也同步推出了适配 iPhone Xs、iPhone Xs Max 和 iPhone XR 的手机保护壳。包括 NËXT 系列、SLɅM系列和 FRĒ 系列。</p><p>SLɅM 系列首次采用时尚的透明图案外观，极简而百搭，同时可突显 iPhone 新品系列流畅的边框线条。这个系列新品集时尚性与功能性于一身，将防摔、防尘与防雪的专业保护和轻薄设计完美结合。通空屏幕设计可让用户直接触控手机屏，防坠落功能和接口防尘盖设计为新 iPhone 提供全方位防护。</p><p>FRĒ 系列沿袭了 LifeProof 防水、防摔、防尘、防雪的四重保护技术，采用两片式设计，内置防刮屏幕膜，支持防水密封，可在 2 米深的水下正常使用长达一小时。接口防尘盖可有效防止充电口和麦克风受到尘土侵扰。售价 318 元起，<a href=\"https://lifeproof.tmall.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222619jrOKfokNiuQal1vM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.872152\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809252226194YG9nvibBEAwpeDV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.193671\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809252226194m0GOYQEbW6SgMNB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.832911\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809252226191r4wxPDBhl5Z9RJE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.858228\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222619mq4op651JvHYsPnd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.887342\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Ambra Pendant by Studio davidpompa</h3><p>去年，墨西哥设计品牌 Studio davidpompa 发布了 Ambra 系列照明。现在，他们推出了 Ambra 系列的新品吊灯，继续探索材料的对比和不同比例混合后的效果。</p><p>这款吊坠拥有优雅的几何轮廓，两个圆柱形状由粉红色的坎特拉玫瑰石制成，这是一种特殊的火山岩，处于自顶部垂坠而下的拉丝铜圆柱的末端。不管是独立悬挂或多重配置，吊灯都能营造出醒目的雕塑般的光线。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222645SX47t2wQgquF3Whv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.181250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809252226455gINwmsp7TW4KuZ8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685937\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222645WyYBZeG9uxa1c8R5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.154688\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222645ujInUe3X4vgJVzdx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222646nU1AhTaF3xmELf4l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.720313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222646Utxc5AEzSZrTw6Pl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.555469\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.davidpompa.com/events/ambra-pandant-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Studio davidpompa</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The Bamba Collection by Carolina Ortega</h3><p>工业设计师 Carolina Ortega 推出了一系列座椅，The Bamba 系列的灵感源自她的家乡哥伦比亚，这是一组展示哥伦比亚传统编织艺术的家具。Bamba 是一个当地词汇，意为“雄伟的树”，意味着成长和变化。</p><p>通过 The Bamba，Carolina Ortega 希望为用户提供机会和空间来自我反思他们的生活和经历。手工编织的纺织品受到哥伦比亚文化艺术的启发，旨在象征平衡，就像我们内在的自我与我们生活的世界之间的平衡一样。整个系列由塑料、铝、木材等混合材料制成，但点睛元素是各种五颜六色的纺织线。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018092522272829dlkBVcQ37yY0mv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222728eUWVPzsKrDoy8TAO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497880\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222728XEbD5CI6ugjmThZk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222729gs0pvNMx2l9XAyhW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497880\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222729pcexEJIdYfFD5CK2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.747959\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222729b50MOC7BLNonr93p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222729M70Rfxujmkpd4qLg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667969\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.carolina-ortega.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Carolina Ortega</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Up Memory Tower by Anton Repponen</h3><p>Mac 电脑系列不像其他厂家那样方便自主更换存储空间， 设计师 Anton Repponen 提出了一种贴心的解决方案。</p><p>他为需要大容量存储的人们设计了一款外置存储盘，不同厚度的圆盘存储容量不同，按需购置，放在桌面上就如同粮仓一样为你提供超大空间。它很像是我们小时候把玩具积木堆积起来的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222816ErVqbzfO47QZvwJ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.822656\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809252228161pbK9CBkRxcY647m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.730469\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222816v7AIfg9QxaTodlLN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222816B6nsc7gRHalwYuVO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222816WFk7udi0LjNSOT8g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222817a9BZXYTPjsl57rhz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925222817W7NLab9UsPyKhQqJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.456250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://work.repponen.com/UP-Memory-Tower\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Anton Repponen</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}